{"tid":2268234,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"Irene扮大牌爭議餘波 SBS電視台刪Red Velvet表演鏡頭","createTime":"2020-11-02T15:40:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-03T02:56:35.000Z","uid":16659,"like":3,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"c1ae3d8bd2a465096310cd0ab306a303591881dc","tid":2268234,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T15:40:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/V-NcJZlmpvywqsfx2KKmnZQ-bT0=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/6HL4NG3LI5D5PAIFM2WIVYSM5U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FV-NcJZlmpvywqsfx2KKmnZQ-bT0%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F6HL4NG3LI5D5PAIFM2WIVYSM5U.jpg&h=47dc13c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nIrene（左二）早前爆出扮大牌爭議。<br />\n韓國女團Red Velvet的29歲隊長Irene上月23日被爆扮大牌，刁難一名擁有15年經驗的韓國時尚雜誌編輯兼造型師A某，Irene當晚在IG發文道歉，但仍然未能平息風波，早前不只連累Red Velvet活動被取消，亦被音樂節目刪鏡頭。<br />\n<br />\n「2020江南音樂節永東大路K-pop演唱會」於上月18日舉行，當時Red Velvet壓軸登場，又跳又唱《Psycho》、《Bad Boy》等多首歌曲，不過相關演唱會昨晚在SBS電視台播出時，所有Red Velvet表演的鏡頭就被刪走，引起網民熱議，推測跟Irene扮大牌爭議有關。<br />\n<br />\n隨後SBS否認刪走鏡頭與Irene的爭議有關：「Red Velvet的演出順序是在最後，因要配合播出時間所以被剪輯，希望大家諒解，大家可透過官方YouTube頻道看Red Velvet的演出。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/a4PwYXWz8SSJ4SbYQW9nMaZZlm8=/802x538/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/3YLSX4YNQJD5RLATKK7FECEGYE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fa4PwYXWz8SSJ4SbYQW9nMaZZlm8%3D%2F802x538%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F3YLSX4YNQJD5RLATKK7FECEGYE.jpg&h=c444f3b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/5NZV5nJMgn2EakAcRqGceyofovA=/802x583/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/PIZVR4WB5RHJ5GH6EY4HRSWDYU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F5NZV5nJMgn2EakAcRqGceyofovA%3D%2F802x583%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FPIZVR4WB5RHJ5GH6EY4HRSWDYU.jpg&h=a306a2fd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"df574a14d0bae0e7b1ae079a674797897fa91487","tid":2268234,"uid":374048,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T15:41:42.000Z","msg":"咁玩法 隨時冇得去mama<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"202915bcc983a00933a4884466df3707e937ad42","tid":2268234,"uid":320204,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T15:41:51.000Z","msg":"Red velvet其他成員好似有啲慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1403d69ba5e713282bfd4339d39d5a396508d586","tid":2268234,"uid":89931,"like":4,"dislike":10,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T15:42:16.000Z","msg":"唔反SBS 了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"261a7600787b2472d42718919ab1ae9f9ef9af03","tid":2268234,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"202915bcc983a00933a4884466df3707e937ad42","tid":2268234,"uid":320204,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T15:41:51.000Z","msg":"Red velvet其他成員好似有啲慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T15:45:28.000Z","msg":"一個累全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8848ee04e1fbe8c0ef3c0bd57d5ca2f6d5d3fad","tid":2268234,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"df574a14d0bae0e7b1ae079a674797897fa91487","tid":2268234,"uid":374048,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T15:41:42.000Z","msg":"咁玩法 隨時冇得去mama<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T15:45:52.000Z","msg":"唔會下話<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a